headline: Q2 Earnings Review: Air Freight and Logistics Stocks Led by Expeditors (NYSE:EXPD)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at air freight and logistics stocks, starting with Expeditors (NYSE:EXPD).
